      "options": {
        "content": "### \u2139\ufe0f About This Report\nProgram and purse configuration from FIS CCX (Client Configuration XTRACT) v1.17. Sourced from **`dim_subprogram`**, **`dim_purse_config`**, and **`dim_package`**. This is the authoritative FIS view of how RFU's program is configured \u2014 purse limits, spend categories, and package definitions as FIS has them. Click any tile to see the detail.\n\n| Table | Source Record | Meaning |\n|---|---|---|\n| `dim_subprogram` | CCX DSPG | Subprogram definition \u2014 program ID, client, market segment, reload rules |\n| `dim_purse_config` | CCX DPUR | Per-purse limits and eligible spend category codes |\n| `dim_package` | CCX DPKG | Card package definition linked to BIN |\n\n**Spend category codes:** 5D=Food/Beverages \u00b7 5A=OTC/Health \u00b7 OF=OTC (OF) \u00b7 OV=OTC (OV) \u00b7 5X=Produce\n\n> Configuration snapshot as of **2026-03-31** for subprogram **26071** (RFU Oregon Medicaid Food).",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "pluginVersion": "10.4.3"
    },
